-- Petrobras Expects to Spend $75 Billion on Oil Rigs by 2020, Folha Reports
-- Helder Marinho
-- 2010-04-23T11:26:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-23/petrobras-expects-to-spend-75-billion-on-oil-rigs-by-2020-folha-reports.html

          
          
             Petroleo Brasileiro SA will spend
at least $75 billion to build 25 new rigs for offshore oil
production and storage by 2020, Folha de S. Paulo reported,
citing Chief Executive Officer Jose Sergio Gabrielli.  
 Almost half of the new rigs will be used to explore
offshore pre-salt fields in Brazilâ€™s Santos Basin, the newspaper
said.   
